comments: THEEEEEEE BEST CSCI professor at hunter. very clear. extremely helpful. interesting lectures. took him for a 2 credit class. learned more about linux/unix, perl, php, python than in any other classes i\'ve ever taken. he\'s a must take professor. not sure if he teaches at hunter anymore though.
Excellent professor. Very clear and helpful, challenging but do-able assignments. No BS. very interesting lectures. Highly recommended.
